'''''Hospital Hustle''''' (formerly titled ''Sarah's Emergency Room'') is a video game developed and published by GameInvest. The player controls Sarah, a recent graduate nurse. Sarah’s first job is to manage the waiting room of a small town hospital. The faster and better she directs the patients to the correct doctor the more experience she gets and the happier the patients become. Sarah keeps moving up to bigger and busier hospitals as the player progresses in the game.
